                     <interp inst="t17940430-34-off173" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17940430-34-off173" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17940430-34-victim351" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Sharp
                        <interp inst="t17940430-34-victim351" type="surname" value="Sharp"></interp>
