                        <interp inst="t17940430-34-victim351" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940430-34-off173 t17940430-34-victim351"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                   about the hour of two in the night, on the <rs id="t17940430-34-cd174" type="crimeDate">4th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940430-34-off173 t17940430-34-cd174"></join>, and burglariously stealing therein, a jack towel, value 2d. a worsted night cap, value 6d. a pair of worsted stockings, value 6d. a pair of cotton stockings, value 6d. two iron chains, value 1s. 6d. seven pewter plates, value 5s. an iron wedge, value 1s. 6d. a brass dog collar, value 2d. the goods of 
                     <persName id="t17940430-34-person352">
                        John
                         Sharp
                     <interp inst="t17940430-34-person352" type="surname" value="Sharp"></interp>
